Package com.matrixone.apps.domain

Provides domain classes and interfaces for the VCP applications.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DomainConstants  
DomainSymbolicConstants The DomainSymbolicConstants interface defines all the symbolic names as static final Strings.
ImageHolder The ImageHolder interface represents a business object that manages documents (attachments).
Job.BackgroundJob Any program that wants to be invoked in the background should implement this interface.
 

Class Summary
CurrencyConversion The CurrencyConversion class represents the Currency Conversion type in the AEF.
DomainObject The DomainObject class represents the top level class for the AEF java classes.
DomainRelationship The DomainRelationship class represents the top level class for the AEF relationship java classes.
FrameworkStringResource This class is used as a set of keys associated with strings stored in separate resource bundles.
Image The Image class represents the top level class for the AEF java classes.
Job The Job Represents a Background Job object in the databse.
JobMonitorTask Timer Task to perform 'Job Status' check as well as update progress.
UnitConversion The UnitConversion class represents the Unit Conversion type in the AEF.
 

Package com.matrixone.apps.domain Description

Provides domain classes and interfaces for the VCP applications.
